articles.title: More Than a Third of New Jersey Residents Reluctant to Get Safe Covid-19 Vaccine
articles.description: Some 36% of New Jersey residents said they wouldn’t be vaccinated for Covid-19 when a safe vaccine is available, according to a survey, despite a second surge of new cases in the state.
